data.description: Exceptional luxury 5 bedroom 4 bath home in the highly sought after neighborhood of Kingston Estates. This home features a spacious open floor plan with spectacular attention to detail and plenty of high-end upgrades and finishes throughout. The thoughtfully landscaped backyard was built to entertain, relax, and enjoy providing a custom-built pool and patio with low maintenance artificial grass and plenty of space to enjoy the peaceful wooded scenery. Your main floor has convenient LVP flooring throughout featuring a  stunning kitchen as the focal point with beautiful finishes such as the custom quartz countertops overlooking your spacious living room making it an amazing entertaining space! The formal dining room, additional sunroom, and a downstairs bedroom  provides so much space and flexibility! Upstairs you will continue to find high end custom finishes and attention to detail!  Walk into the bedroom of your dreams with a spacious primary bedroom and luxury bathroom experience.
